title: Russell Wilson injured in loss to Rams, Jets and Falcons in London, Nate Burleson, NFL Week 5 picks!
itunes:title: Russell Wilson injured in loss to Rams, Jets and Falcons in London, Nate Burleson, NFL Week 5 picks!
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Michael Robinson discuss the Rams victory over the Seahawks and update the injury to Russell Wilson's finger. Melissa Stark gives us the latest from London preparing for Jets-Falcons on Sunday morning while Nate Burleson recalls his best memory from playing overseas. We deliver the best Week 5 matchup breakdowns while Kay gives you her Top Five Fantasy Football players and our Pigskin Picks!

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
